"well, if I have to
look like somebody,

19:00.306 --> 19:01.839
I'm so glad
it's aunt harper."

19:01.841 --> 19:04.175
I mean, is she just
a timeless beauty, or what?

19:04.177 --> 19:06.410
And--and so talented.

19:06.412 --> 19:09.180
Aunt marjorie always
called her "superstar."

19:09.182 --> 19:10.915
I really hate to break up
the family reunion,

19:10.917 --> 19:13.351
But we have
a rehearsal dinner
nightmare on our hands.

19:13.353 --> 19:15.786
See?
Oh, gosh, these
italian family feuds.

19:15.788 --> 19:17.555
They last for 700 years.

19:17.557 --> 19:19.490
And I don't know where I'm gonna
put my great-aunt birdie.

19:19.492 --> 19:21.259
She came in
all the way from boston.

19:21.261 --> 19:25.196
Interesting color scheme.
Is that...Puce?

19:25.198 --> 19:27.398
Bold choice.

19:27.400 --> 19:29.667
I thought your mom said
you were going with

19:29.669 --> 19:32.203
Dusky rose
and gold accents.

19:32.205 --> 19:34.205
No, that's what her mom
<i>wanted</i> her to go with.

19:34.207 --> 19:36.174
Pink and gold are classics.

19:36.176 --> 19:37.241
Old-fashioned.

19:37.243 --> 19:39.210
Tasteful.
Boring.

19:43.782 --> 19:45.316
Oh, my gosh!

19:45.318 --> 19:47.885
Debbie,
you fixed it!
Thank you!

19:47.887 --> 19:51.289
Oh! You have <i>got</i> to come
to my bachelorette party.

19:51.291 --> 19:52.823
Bachelorette party?

19:52.825 --> 19:56.227
Oh, yeah, we're family.
You have to come.

19:56.229 --> 19:58.596
We have champagne
and mani-pedi's.
Mani-pedi's.

19:58.598 --> 20:00.331
Yay!
Yay!

20:00.333 --> 20:02.600
Well, I'll get
settled in, then.

20:02.602 --> 20:03.901
Okay.
All right.
All right.

20:03.903 --> 20:06.871
We'll see you
for mani-pedi's.

20:06.873 --> 20:08.573
All: Mani-pedi's!

20:11.310 --> 20:12.410
Amanda!

20:12.412 --> 20:14.612
