What have you got?

20:14.614 --> 20:17.215
We have a bigger problem.

20:17.217 --> 20:20.218
I spoke to the investors.

20:20.220 --> 20:21.686
Amanda, the tonic.

20:21.688 --> 20:23.487
Harper, this is serious.

20:23.489 --> 20:25.923
You need to come home
right now. I can't do this.

20:25.925 --> 20:30.361
I am in a situation here,
amanda. I need information.

20:30.363 --> 20:32.230
What kind of situation?
