What are you <i>doing?</i>

26:50.343 --> 26:52.309
The sun is very bad
for your skin.

26:52.311 --> 26:55.679
So, mirabella, tell me
about this french guy.

26:55.681 --> 26:57.281
Did you think
you were in love with him?

26:57.283 --> 27:00.818
Okay, uh, no.
I mean, it was
a great experience,

27:00.820 --> 27:03.053
But it wasn't like
how it is with marco.

27:03.055 --> 27:06.657
Right. Marco.
The playboy prince.

27:06.659 --> 27:10.194
I'm sorry. I just--
I read that.

27:10.196 --> 27:13.263
He retired that title
when he met me. Besides,
he's not a real prince.

27:13.265 --> 27:16.033
( laughter )
but he is a real italian.

27:16.035 --> 27:18.235
I wouldn't worry too much
about that, though.

27:18.237 --> 27:21.405
Not every italian guy
has to have a mistress,
right?

27:21.407 --> 27:24.074
Right?
I'm not worried about it.

27:24.076 --> 27:28.245
I knew marco was the right guy
right from the very beginning.

