Hello?
<i>Harper?</i>

29:59.198 --> 30:00.964
Any good news, amanda?

30:00.966 --> 30:03.200
Okay. Okay, okay.

30:03.202 --> 30:05.035
<i>The good news.</i>
<i>The trunk that the tonic</i>

30:05.037 --> 30:08.105
Was found in was owned
by some old vaudeville guy,

30:08.107 --> 30:09.973
Tom dorian.
<i>Never heard of him.</i>
<i>Is that it?</i>

30:09.975 --> 30:12.176
And now the not-so-good news.

30:12.178 --> 30:14.812
The investors found out about
mirabella leaving the show.

30:14.814 --> 30:17.447
Oh, no! How?!
<i>One of the dancers</i>

30:17.449 --> 30:19.116
Spilled, and it gets worse.

30:19.118 --> 30:21.185
They're going to recast her.

30:21.187 --> 30:22.920
They can't do that.
<i>Yes,</i>

30:22.922 --> 30:24.421
They can. Look,

30:24.423 --> 30:25.989
<i>I told the investors</i>

30:25.991 --> 30:27.391
<i>Mirabella'd be back</i>
<i>for rehearsal on Monday,</i>

30:27.393 --> 30:29.827
But if mirabella is not
back here for it,

30:29.829 --> 30:32.996
They're going to replace her.
And you.

30:32.998 --> 30:35.933
We don't need a new lead.
Mirabella is coming back.

30:35.935 --> 30:37.267
( laughing )
whoo!

30:37.269 --> 30:39.169
And they wouldn't dare
replace me.

30:39.171 --> 30:40.571
Why am I scared?

30:40.573 --> 30:42.039
Don't say anything to anybody.

30:42.041 --> 30:43.240
Tell them I will
be back on Monday

30:43.242 --> 30:44.975
<i>With our star.</i>

30:44.977 --> 30:47.010
