look me in the eye
and tell me the truth--

49:02.507 --> 49:06.542
Do you love my daughter?
Absolutely.
With all my heart, sir.

49:06.544 --> 49:10.112
All right, then.
I can help you fix this,

49:10.114 --> 49:12.214
