reasonable explanation.

51:00.458 --> 51:03.559
There is <i>nothing</i>
<i>reasonable about this--</i>
<i>or you.</i>

51:03.561 --> 51:05.361
Okay, just take
a deep breath--

51:05.363 --> 51:08.130
